ironically is not affected by elementary teachers' dispute. RICK CORRALES / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, Protesting members of Whittier Elementary Teachers Assn. 
lead their union colleagues in a song. EUGENE TANNER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
