<P>
The "Carousel Goes Hog Wild" comedy show and dinner Feb. 2 at the Irvine 
Improvisation in Irvine raised an estimated $12,000 for the Carousel chapter of 
the Guilds of the Orange County Performing Arts Center. Lu-an Cohen and Carol 
Mock were chairwomen. 
</P>
