raised an estimated $30,000 for the Catholic Charities of Orange County. Doris 
Cantley was chairwoman. 
</P>
<P>
The "Carnival of Holidays" dinner Feb. 4 at the Disneyland Hotel in Anaheim 
raised an estimated $15,000 for the Masked Ball chapter of the Guilds of the 
Orange County Performing Arts Center. Susan Levine was chairwoman. 
</P>
