SWISS, AUSTRIANS LEAD ON BOBSLEDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times staff and wire wire service reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
CORTINO DAMPEZZO, Italy 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Switzerland II and Austria I dominated the second-to-last day of qualifying 
runs in the four-man competition Wednesday night at the World Bobsled 
Championships. 
</P>
<P>
In the first run, Switzerland II, driven by Gustav Weder, finished first in 
